{"tid":1862241,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"全港投注站無限期關閉　直至另行通知！","createTime":"2020-02-04T13:53:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-04T14:23:26.000Z","uid":20933,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"ec4f17a8478dff4f34fe7241b26e07788d27eca9","tid":1862241,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T13:53:38.000Z","msg":"武漢肺炎疫情持續擴散，馬會這天（4日）表示，為配合香港各界作出的共同努力，將會加強預防措施。<br />\n<br />\n政府日前表示，未來兩星期將會是香港能否控制疫情及防止社區爆發的關鍵時刻，馬會決定，為未來關鍵兩星期採取下列進一步措施，避免疫情進一步擴散。<br />\n<br />\n1. 全港共101間場外投注處將即時無限期停止服務，直至另行通知。換言之原定明日（5日）將會全港營業的投注站，如今變為將會關閉，而非原定的明日朝九晚五營業。<br />\n<br />\n2. 由2月6日（星期四）起，電話投注熱線包括1881、1882、1883、1884、1885、1887、1889、「優越」紅卡及各快線服務將會暫時停止服務，馬迷顧客可繼續使用1886電話投注自動服務系統、流動應用程式、Racing Touch或網上投注區進行賽馬及足球投注。詳情請瀏覽： <a href=\"https://is.hkjc.com/fund_transfer_mobile/en/index.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fis.hkjc.com%2Ffund_transfer_mobile%2Fen%2Findex.html&d=iVnpHeK512wFMD%2FK5G8l3WhNlLB%2BLbsdBqu6cuXqlDc%3D&h=08655195\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://is.hkjc.com/fund_transfer_mobile/en/index.html</a> 。"},{"pid":"77b53cae9b5a880bc29857518e001d4f29b3fdcb","tid":1862241,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T13:54:18.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.sports.appledaily.com/racing/20200204/LGDQVSUBZKWIWO7FXZZUZILX5E/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.sports.appledaily.com%2Fracing%2F20200204%2FLGDQVSUBZKWIWO7FXZZUZILX5E%2F&d=iVnpHeK512wFMD%2FK5G8l3WhNlLB%2BLbsdBqu6cuXqlDc%3D&h=0aeb1487\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.sports.appledaily.com%2Fracing%2F20200204%2FLGDQVSUBZKWIWO7FXZZUZILX5E%2F&h=d3214573\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.sports.appledaily.com/racing/20200204/LGDQVSUBZKWIWO7FXZZUZILX5E/</a>"},{"pid":"0b9d1504976677fe4d8f00d8f5110453bd0c2bf4","tid":1862241,"uid":153318,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T13:56:03.000Z","msg":"仲諗住聽日入錢賭馬<img src=\"/asset